# 📊 Revenue vs Target

This Power BI dashboard offers a comprehensive overview of the company's financial health, enabling stakeholders to monitor key performance indicators and make informed decisions.​

## Key Features:

Revenue & Profit Analysis: Visualizes total revenue, costs, expenses, and net profit, providing insights into financial performance over time.​

Top 5 Clients: Identifies the top five clients contributing to revenue, helping to focus on key customer relationships.​

Payments by Type: Breaks down payments received by type (e.g., credit card, bank transfer), offering a clear view of payment distribution.​

Monthly Profit Trends: Displays profit trends on a monthly basis, allowing for the identification of patterns and anomalies.

